{"tid":2491372,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"SpaceX「星鏈」將顛覆網路未來 馬斯克預告：今夏結束 Beta 測試版","createTime":"2021-04-16T09:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T10:16:24.000Z","uid":295230,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"07ab2191fe9bf0230a45f08eb9e3c6479a9ae219","tid":2491372,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:11:46.000Z","msg":"美國航太製造商 SpaceX 先前推出衛星網路服務「星鏈計畫」（Starlink），期待為全球帶來高速網路。執行長馬斯克（Elon Musk）不久前在推特上宣布，由於發展出乎意料地快，預計今年夏季結束前就會退出 Beta 測試模式。此外，服務很快就會升級，可改善網路的連接範圍，並藉由衛星天線實現「完全移動化」的目標。<br />\n<br />\n星鏈計畫發展迅速，光是今年一月初提供有限的公開 Beta 版服務，就收到大量的排隊名單。另外，除了大幅降低設備製造商的製造成本，SpaceX 還用比製造成本低 1,000 美元的價格出售衛星天線。<br />\n<br />\n根據 SpaceX 官網，衛星天線最初價格為 499 美元，每個月需支付 99 美元 Wi-Fi 服務費，但其製造技術的成本約為 1,500 美元，即使扣除 Wi-Fi 月租費，每賣出一顆衛星天線，公司就可能損失至少近 500 美元。但馬斯克表示「成本正迅速下降」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1381273474400800773?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1381273474400800773%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2021%2F04%2F13%2Fcost-of-spacex-starlink-dish-decreasing-rapidly-elon-musk-says%2F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1381273474400800773%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1381273474400800773%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ftechnews.tw%252F2021%252F04%252F13%252Fcost-of-spacex-starlink-dish-decreasing-rapidly-elon-musk-says%252F&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=b5ba2670\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1381273474400800773%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1381273474400800773%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ftechnews.tw%252F2021%252F04%252F13%252Fcost-of-spacex-starlink-dish-decreasing-rapidly-elon-musk-says%252F&h=b87eada5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1381273474400800773?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1381273474400800773%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2021%2F04%2F13%2Fcost-of-spacex-starlink-dish-decreasing-rapidly-elon-musk-says%2F</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>計畫今夏結束 Beta 測試</strong><br />\n根據馬斯克的最新推文，自從公開測試之後，星鏈網路的延遲（latency）、頻寬（bandwidth）和服務正常運行時間不斷在改善，今年夏天很可能退出 Beta 測試模式，這也表示將首次發布其完整版本。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/thesheetztweetz/status/1382748455341322242?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1382839546484641794%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es2_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2021%2F04%2F16%2Felon-musk-starlink-internet-beta-ends-summer-aims-fully-mobile%2F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthesheetztweetz%2Fstatus%2F1382748455341322242%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1382839546484641794%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es2_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ftechnews.tw%252F2021%252F04%252F16%252Felon-musk-starlink-internet-beta-ends-summer-aims-fully-mobile%252F&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=951717ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthesheetztweetz%2Fstatus%2F1382748455341322242%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1382839546484641794%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es2_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ftechnews.tw%252F2021%252F04%252F16%252Felon-musk-starlink-internet-beta-ends-summer-aims-fully-mobile%252F&h=3f483459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/thesheetztweetz/status/1382748455341322242?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1382839546484641794%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es2_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2021%2F04%2F16%2Felon-musk-starlink-internet-beta-ends-summer-aims-fully-mobile%2F</a><br />\n外媒預測，完整發行版有兩種可能，星鏈網路可能比以往任何時候都快，各地區居民跟這個世界以外的地方連接，但也可能因為升級到完整版，服務無法負荷一整天的使用人數，導致網速變慢。目前，SpaceX 為了發射更多衛星來增強其網路服務，所以也預計短期內處理這個問題。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>星鏈計畫的未來想像</strong><br />\n對於星鏈計畫的未來想像，推特帳號「Everyday Astronaut」也詢問馬斯克，未來是否不會只局限在同個地方，抑或是必須放在車上到處跑？馬斯克回覆，今年底應該可以實現「完全移動化」的目標，可以將其移到任何地方，也可以放到露營車或正在移動的卡車。不過，目前仍需要多發射幾次衛星提升覆蓋率，並且升級關鍵軟體。<br />\n<br />\n換言之，未來網路不會像一般家庭網路一樣必須綁在一起，馬斯克的聲明也透露，訂閱星鏈網路服務只需要綁定一個人的名字或帳戶，只要他擁有一顆衛星天線接收器，並將其插入電源就能在任何地方使用高速網路。"},{"pid":"64a095899150da6dac6aaacd1ba9011b56ca6eca","tid":2491372,"uid":73241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"大爆升？"},{"pid":"98ee8a1dbbde0946bf3f842e0f5b5b3a0d27fd1f","tid":2491372,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:12:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2021/04/16/elon-musk-starlink-internet-beta-ends-summer-aims-fully-mobile/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2021%2F04%2F16%2Felon-musk-starlink-internet-beta-ends-summer-aims-fully-mobile%2F&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=a79cf483\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2021/04/16/elon-musk-starlink-internet-beta-ends-summer-aims-fully-mobile/</a>"},{"pid":"179624d9982b5d5bc7d4d50167b0697b8e0afed0","tid":2491372,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64a095899150da6dac6aaacd1ba9011b56ca6eca","tid":2491372,"uid":73241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"大爆升？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:12:32.000Z","msg":"Fair price 50<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d959921066b9dbf44e0dea5e30c2c847b53aa5ce","tid":2491372,"uid":36441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:16:11.000Z","msg":"船公司用應該抵過而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53561406122b6c9fcfc434a6c25069a4899196d7","tid":2491372,"uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d959921066b9dbf44e0dea5e30c2c847b53aa5ce","tid":2491372,"uid":36441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":